"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## What is Balancer?\\nBalancer is an automated market maker (AMM) protocol that allows users to swap assets using liquidity pools, similar to Uniswap. Balancer differs from Uniswap in that liquidity pools can have up to 8 assets deposited in them, and the desired ratio between those assets can be set by the person that creates it. This allows users to create custom investment vehicles that can act like index funds, which comes with the added benefit of being able to maintain the ratios of the assets in their portfolio by having arbitragers effectively manage the fund for them.\\n\\n## Using Balancer on Polygon\\nIn this tutorial, we will cover how to swap on Balancer on the Polygon network. Polygon is an EVM smart contract-enabled side chain that is very similar to Ethereum. This means that you can use familiar tools like MetaMask to approve transactions. An added benefit is that the transaction fees on Polygon are much lower than on Ethereum.\\n\\nIn order to use Balancer on Polygon, you'll need to have assets on Polygon. You can do this by using a bridge, which you can find here: [Ethereum <> Polygon bridge](https://wallet.matic.network/bridge/).\\n\\nIf this is your first time using Polygon, check out [this guide](https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/Hm0zb1vkvx0yoj9EfvqCt119vsMdcD0Cp9Sk25hyNic).\\n\\n## How to swap on Balancer\\n\\n**Step 1: Go to Balancer**\\n\\nTo access Balancer on the Polygon network, go to [https://polygon.balancer.fi](https://polygon.balancer.fi).\\n\\n**Step 2: Connect your wallet**\\n\\nMake sure your wallet is on the Polygon Network. If you‚Äôre using MetaMask, it should look like this. You can use the dropdown to toggle between networks.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/b912031e-0fbd-4314-9d9f-aa0abd2a3d27.png?height=694&width=710)\\n\\nOn the Balancer page, click ‚ÄúConnect wallet‚Äù.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/96930f0d-5019-480c-a6ac-aa6845ede97d.png?height=1794&width=2756)\\n\\nSelect the wallet you‚Äôd like to use.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8c7815ad-5e9f-4524-af83-d94d18f36e13.png?height=1788&width=2754)\\n\\n**Step 3: Go to ‚ÄúTrade‚Äù**\\n\\nNow that your wallet is connected, you can swap on Balancer. To do this, select ‚ÄúTrade‚Äù at the top of the page.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/325fec49-a0b1-489e-920b-657644d4b570.png?height=1794&width=2756)\\n\\n**Step 4: Swap**\\n\\nIn the Balancer interface, enter the token and amount you‚Äôd like to send and receive. Then select ‚ÄúPreview Trade‚Äù.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/d346b95e-e0c8-4baf-b1f0-41d317e248aa.png?height=1796&width=2758)\\n\\nNext you‚Äôll need to approve the swap, which gives Balancer access to the funds you are sending (in my case, USDT). You might need to wait a minute or two for this transaction to complete.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/adb0e27a-2f7d-4641-bd8e-48480876135f.png?height=1792&width=2754)\\n\\nOnce the ‚ÄúApprove‚Äù transaction completes, you will be prompted to confirm the trade. Click ‚ÄúConfirm trade‚Äù.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/38ee716f-2cd1-47d7-8627-ee79ec3ab0d8.png?height=1796&width=2738)\\n\\n**Congrats! You made your first swap on Balancer üéâ**\\nOnce your trade has settled, you should see this message.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/b84ff6d6-c0f6-4faf-987e-e6b45a51f151.png?height=1794&width=2758)\\n\\n*This guide was written in collaboration with [@JorrinB](https://twitter.com/JorrinB).*\\n\\n[Balancer Pathfinder Guide](split://0x54496045c12264B3A3E8aa5d0BA71094eC901775?network=mainnet)\",\"timestamp\":1629130095,\"title\":\"Tutorial: How to swap on Balancer (Polygon)\",\"publication\":\"rabbithole\"},\"digest\":\"gGZ-PSzUBsCgWvEmy-fE3Sx1JNnwYa0ojji-RSCd2p8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x51448923d8a215a5A8cd872a51f22c2f5c43b444\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"uW4DGWXK3AAF365Yjexi2J8VkihORBbmK5Ie3u4ctEw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"F9YGAuHnQYjMs1hhAPEZ-iMtiAmFwvRUjLl-lt_LYCg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"MyFFVAWY0UhRtcH9h7S06g4J99KCH3fzE3z0Oh6HW1UKCH4ydRXayhOAa4_bjr-u2g7Sq6e74TW9nPBp27dd-A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x56602a79ddd97b2a764781eb576368f11ba6ab656a3496ac4265c361fa14d47f0bce8aab108dab79908a28d91ee87d1263a9627dd649b8b746af593c461e811b1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on rabbithole.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"uW4DGWXK3AAF365Yjexi2J8VkihORBbmK5Ie3u4ctEw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"F9YGAuHnQYjMs1hhAPEZ-iMtiAmFwvRUjLl-lt_LYCg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"fwDeEvyMeTzuqQ8Kz1jv34tgbsBEKqfP3ZehkjWYUIg\"}"